    • registerAndSubmitPharmacyEnrollment

      public void registerAndSubmitPharmacyEnrollment​(java.lang.String testEmailAccount, java.lang.String enrollmentType, java.lang.String newEmail, java.lang.String firstName, java.lang.String lastName, java.lang.String statusOfApplication, java.lang.String paymentOption, java.lang.String medicareParticipant, java.lang.String taxonomyCategory, java.lang.String taxonomy) throws java.lang.Exception
      This method registers a new Provider. Creates and submits a pharmacy enrollment. The flow is first deletes all the exiting emails in gmail and then open registration page. Fills in all the fields. Opens gmail, clicks on registration link and confirms. Logs in with the email, selects the enrollment type (pharmacy) and completes all the sections then signs the enrollment. At the end the info writes out to ProviderInfo.xlsx
